2010-11-11 10:38  gaede

	* [r1815] Analysis/RecoMCTruthLink/src/RecoMCTruthLinker.cc:
	  protected against missing track or cluster collections (e.g.
	  still create track relation if clusters missing)

2010-10-29 12:44  engels

	* [r1796] .: created branch v00-19-pre

2010-10-29 10:29  engels

	* [r1795] fixed latex typo (same fix as in r1321 and r1335)

2010-10-18 15:32  gaede

	* [r1787] added RecoMcTruthLink doc

2010-10-18 14:22  gaede

	* [r1786] updated default values of steering parameters to work
	  with standard reconstruction

2010-10-15 14:09  aplin

	* [r1783] Smearing has been re-written for the VXD. Smearing is
	  still performed along the ladders if they are found to exist in
	  the GEAR file, otherwise cylindrical smearing is performed. This
	  can be forced by setting the steering parameter
	  _smearAlongLadders to 0. Hits which are found to not be within
	  the width of the sensitive layer as stated in the GEAR file are
	  dropped.

2010-10-15 00:10  berggren

	* [r1781] RecoMCTruthLinker: complete linking of all contributing
	  true particles.
	  Also links from Tracks, Clusters, and CalorimeterHits. Fixed that
	  the wrong True particle sometimes was linked to CalorimeterHits:
	  the linked particle was not the one entering the Calorimeter, but
	  a particle later in the shower.
	  Added a sample steering-stanza xml-snippet.

