2008-11-13 10:18  aplin

	* [r1269] added the event number to the debug output statment

2008-11-13 10:17  aplin

	* [r1268] changed some "IF(X.NE.0.AND.Y(X).EQ.Z)" to "IF(A.NE.0)
	  THEN IF(Y(A).EQ.Z)", this allows the array out of bounds checking
	  to funtion properly, for an acceptable small overhead in
	  performace. As a temporary fix increased LILLY in tflnks and
	  IBUFF in tfcand to 1000. This will stop the crashes for now but
	  some protection is needed.

